---
// 不需要任何服务器端逻辑，这是一个纯静态页面
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AstroWeb - 个人网站管理系统</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #3498db;
            --secondary-color: #2980b9;
            --accent-color: #f39c12;
            --text-color: #2c3e50;
            --light-bg: #f5f7fa;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            color: var(--text-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4);
        }
        
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        
        .feature {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 220px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            /* 动画相关样式 */
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.5s ease forwards;
        }
        
        .feature:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
        .feature:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .feature:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.45s; }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .feature:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .feature h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        
        footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">A</div>
        <h1>欢迎使用 AstroWeb</h1>
        <p>
            这是一个功能强大的个人网站管理系统，帮助您轻松管理文章、链接和其他内容。
            使用 Astro 构建，结合现代 Web 技术，提供流畅的使用体验。
        </p>
        <a href="/login" class="btn">进入管理系统</a>
        
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">📝</div>
                <h3>文章管理</h3>
                <p>轻松创建、编辑和组织您的文章，支持 Markdown 格式。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔗</div>
                <h3>链接收藏</h3>
                <p>管理和分类您收藏的网络资源和有用链接。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">🛠️</div>
                <h3>简单易用</h3>
                <p>直观的界面设计，让内容管理变得简单高效。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p>© 2025 AstroWeb - 基于 Astro 构建的现代内容管理系统</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>